Subject: Re: [VB] repro pop-outs help...

Send them back.  All of the repro popouts I've seen were junk.  AFAIK,
there's only one maker of these stateside, sold thru various parts houses.
CE makes them as well, and I imagine theirs are better, but they're
also phat bank.

TJ Stallone wrote:
